<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Site Maintenance</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: system-ui, sans-serif; background-color: #f3f4f6; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; height: 100vh; margin: 0; color: #111827; }
        .container { text-align: center; background: white; padding: 3rem; border-radius: 8px; border-top: 4px solid #d1d5db; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); max-width: 500px; width: 90%; }
        h1 { margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.5rem; }
        p { color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.5; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Website Offline</h1>
        <p>This website is currently undergoing scheduled maintenance and is temporarily unavailable.</p>
        <p>Please check back later.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>